# =================================
# HOW TO SET UP GOOGLE AUTH
# =================================
# 1. Go to Google Cloud Console (https://console.cloud.google.com)
# 2. Create a new project or select existing
# 3. Enable Google+ API and Google Identity Services
# 4. Go to Credentials > Create Credentials > OAuth 2.0 Client ID
# 5. Add authorized redirect URIs:
#    - https://your-project.supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
# 6. Copy Client ID and Client Secret to Supabase:
#    - Authentication > Providers > Google

# =================================
# HOW TO SET UP STRIPE (STEP BY STEP)
# =================================
#
# 1. Go to Stripe Dashboard: https://dashboard.stripe.com
#
# 2. Get your API keys:
#    - Go to Developers > API Keys
#    - Copy the Secret Key (starts with sk_test_ or sk_live_)
#    - Paste it as STRIPE_SECRET_KEY above
#
# 3. Create Products in Stripe:
#    - Go to Products > Add Product
#
#    PRODUCT 1: JumpStudy Pro
#    - Name: JumpStudy Pro
#    - Add Price 1: $15.99 USD, Recurring Monthly
#    - Add Price 2: $127.99 USD, Recurring Yearly
#    - Copy both price IDs (price_xxx) to STRIPE_PRO_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID and STRIPE_PRO_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID
#
#    PRODUCT 2: JumpStudy Student
#    - Name: JumpStudy Student
#    - Add Price 1: $9.99 USD, Recurring Monthly
#    - Add Price 2: $79.99 USD, Recurring Yearly
#    - Copy both price IDs to STRIPE_STUDENT_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID and STRIPE_STUDENT_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID
#
#    PRODUCT 3: JumpStudy Classroom
#    - Name: JumpStudy Classroom
#    - Add Price 1: $12.99 USD, Recurring Monthly (per seat)
#    - Add Price 2: $99.99 USD, Recurring Yearly (per seat)
#    - Copy both price IDs to STRIPE_TEAM_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID and STRIPE_TEAM_ANNUAL_PRICE_ID
#
# 4. Set up Webhooks:
#    - Go to Developers > Webhooks
#    - Click "Add endpoint"
#    - Endpoint URL: https://your-domain.com/api/stripe/webhook
#    - Select events:
#      * checkout.session.completed
#      * customer.subscription.created
#      * customer.subscription.updated
#      * customer.subscription.deleted
#      * invoice.payment_failed
#      * invoice.paid
#    - Copy the Signing Secret (whsec_xxx) to STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
#
# 5. Test with Stripe Test Mode first, then switch to Live when ready!
